{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LibMtFgfZEfUpgpUv5BMtu","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $622.44\n     4→Total API calls: 4621\n     5→Average cost per story: $3.34 (152 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 257,718,666 | $1.50/MTok | $386.58 | 62% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 7,458,643 | $18.75/MTok | $139.85 | 22% |\n    13→| Output | 1,277,872 | $75/MTok | $95.84 | 15% |\n    14→| Input | 11,423 | $15/MTok | $0.17 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 2769 | $349.71 | 56.2% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 505 | $110.89 | 17.8% |\n    22→| retro | 427 | $60.48 | 9.7% |\n    23→| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 5.9% |\n    24→| code-review | 305 | $34.70 | 5.6% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 4.8% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 1998 | $245.89 | 39.5% |\n    32→| Read | 889 | $116.86 | 18.8% |\n    33→| Edit | 581 | $74.10 | 11.9% |\n    34→| Agent | 410 | $54.05 | 8.7% |\n    35→| Skill | 120 | $44.57 | 7.2% |\n    36→| Grep | 275 | $31.96 | 5.1% |\n    37→| Write | 134 | $24.84 | 4.0% |\n    38→| TodoWrite | 105 | $14.40 | 2.3% |\n    39→| Glob | 79 | $12.44 | 2.0% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 26 | $2.90 | 0.5% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 530 | $114.81 | 18.4% |\n    47→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 3.8% |\n    48→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 3.6% |\n    49→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.7% |\n    50→| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 2.0% |\n    51→| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.8% |\n    52→| 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view | 74 | $10.80 | 1.7% |\n    53→| 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning | 75 | $10.27 | 1.6% |\n    54→| 12-4-shared-test-utilities-fixtures | 85 | $9.98 | 1.6% |\n    55→| 8-6-rust-verification-dockerfile | 73 | $9.86 | 1.6% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01XUm8aiE15uDCb7rQdRQ984","session_id":"1d62d690-8737-454d-9d05-a44eb6ba0c17","uuid":"71628fa6-d212-4efe-bce2-ac10c3873ea0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:13:49.522Z"}
