{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01C9LbMfTgtug2RzNdg4JapN","type":"tool_result","content":"  1250→## 7. Action Items\n  1251→\n  1252→| # | Action | Priority | Owner | Status |\n  1253→|---|--------|----------|-------|--------|\n  1254→| 1 | Fix ralph state reconciliation to not overwrite `done` stories back to `review` | HIGH | Infrastructure | OPEN (flagged sessions 1-9) |\n  1255→| 2 | Fix 6 pre-existing BATS test failures (`all_tasks_complete`, `get_current_task`) | MEDIUM | Tech debt | OPEN (flagged sessions 1-9) |\n  1256→| 3 | Standardize proof document format and provide template to verify subagents | MEDIUM | Process | OPEN (flagged sessions 2, 3, 5, 6, 9) |\n  1257→| 4 | Update CODEHARNESS-PATCH template to be tier-aware | MEDIUM | Tech debt | OPEN (from session 8) |\n  1258→| 5 | Address `allFiles()` recreating array per call | LOW | Tech debt backlog | OPEN (from session 8) |\n  1259→| 6 | Reduce \"unknown\" story cost bucket (18.4% unattributed spend) | LOW | Tooling | NEW |\n  1260→| 7 | Plan next epic / sprint — Epic 16 is done, all 16 epics complete | HIGH | PM | NEW |\n  1261→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01XUm8aiE15uDCb7rQdRQ984","session_id":"1d62d690-8737-454d-9d05-a44eb6ba0c17","uuid":"abd8d29e-5b29-4fae-8936-2b7e0b2f3af4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:13:57.671Z"}
